INSERT INTO `stories` VALUES (24,'The Resurrection of the T-Rex','Dr. Sarah Rodriguez and her team bring a T-Rex back to life using the Resurrecto-Tron 3000, but faced with ethical dilemmas, they eventually transport it back to its prehistoric era through a time portal, marking a historic event in the world of science and technology.',26),(25,'The Rise of the Soccer Superstars','Alex and his friends form a soccer team, The Soccer Superstars, and practice hard to win a community tournament, ultimately achieving victory and becoming local heroes.',26),(26,'Max\'s Journey to Rock Stardom','Follow Max\'s journey from a kid dreaming of becoming a rock star, forming a band for a talent show, attending a music camp, and eventually achieving his dream through hard work, dedication, and unwavering belief in himself.',26),(27,'The Mystery of the Stolen Diamond','When the most precious diamond in the world, the Heart of the Ocean, is stolen from a famous museum in the peaceful town of Riverdale, the mayor calls upon a group of young detectives, the Mystery Solvers, to crack the case and catch the notorious jewel thief.',26),(28,'Lily and Spark: Adventures of a Girl and Her Dragon','Follow the heartwarming adventures of Lily and her dragon, Spark, as they help various creatures in need and are honored by the king for their bravery and kindness.',26),(29,'The Voyage of the Starblazer: Exploring the Cosmic Frontier','Join the brave astronauts of the Starblazer as they embark on an incredible journey to a distant planet, encountering awe-inspiring phenomena, making groundbreaking discoveries, and returning to Earth as heroes, inspiring future generations to reach for the stars.',20),(30,'The Concert for New Uniforms: A Story of Teamwork and Triumph','When their school\'s marching band is chosen to perform at the State Marching Band Festival but needs new uniforms, the band members come together to organize a successful concert fundraiser, raise enough money for the uniforms, win first place at the festival, and inspire others with the power of teamwork and creativity.',20),(31,'The Winning Goal','Alex, a passionate ice hockey player, scores a dramatic winning goal for his team, the Ice Dragons, in a thrilling game against the Frosty Falcons, showcasing teamwork and determination.',20),(32,'Sammy the Friendly Shark and the Shiny Sea Treasure','Sammy, the friendly shark, befriends a group of colorful fish and together they discover a shiny treasure chest, which they share with all the sea creatures. As more sea animals join in the fun, they work together to clean up and beautify the coral reef, ultimately making the ocean a better place for all.',20),(33,'Lily\'s Journey to Artistic Success','Follow Lily, a talented painter in New York City, as she befriends a musician, Max, and together they showcase her artwork at a local open mic night, leading to a successful art exhibit and a blossoming career in the vibrant city.',20),(34,'The Brave Young Explorer: Uncovering Captain William\'s Lost Treasure','Thirteen-year-old Jacob uncovers an old treasure map from colonial times, leading him and the museum curator, Ms. Jenkins, to discover the long-lost treasure of Captain William hidden in a secret cave, sparking an excitement for the town\'s history and earning Jacob the title of a brave young explorer.',20),(35,'Lily and Whiskers: A Garden Adventure','A story about a little girl named Lily and her mischievous cat, Whiskers, as they explore a beautiful garden, encountering butterflies, bees, birds, and a ladybug, before heading home, exhausted but content.',26),(36,'Love Across Borders: Madhav and Haley\'s Journey','Madhav and Haley\'s unexpected meeting blossomed into a deep connection that transcended their cultural differences, leading to a love story that defied geographical boundaries and gained the support of both their families.',26);
