INSERT INTO `story_text` VALUES (44,24,'Once upon a time in the future, scientists had invented a machine that could bring dinosaurs back to life. It was a groundbreaking moment in the history of science and technology. The machine was called the Resurrecto-Tron 3000, and it could recreate extinct species by extracting DNA from fossilized remains.',0),(45,24,'The leading paleontologist, Dr. Sarah Rodriguez, was determined to use the Resurrecto-Tron 3000 to bring back the majestic Tyrannosaurus rex, also known as the T-Rex. With the help of her team, Dr. Rodriguez obtained a well-preserved T-Rex fossil and carefully extracted its DNA. After months of hard work and dedication, they successfully activated the Resurrecto-Tron 3000, and to their amazement, a living, breathing T-Rex appeared before their eyes.',1),(46,24,'The news of the T-Rex\'s resurrection spread like wildfire, and people from around the world flocked to witness this extraordinary creature. The once extinct T-Rex had now become a living, breathing celebrity. Everyone marveled at the sight of the enormous and powerful dinosaur.',2),(47,24,'As the T-Rex roamed around its new environment, it became clear that its presence posed a danger to the modern world. Dr. Rodriguez and her team faced a difficult decision: should they continue to keep the T-Rex alive, or should they find a way to safely return it to its own time period? It was a moral and ethical dilemma that weighed heavily on their shoulders.',3),(48,24,'Meanwhile, the government became involved in the situation, expressing concerns about the potential threat the T-Rex posed to public safety. The authorities demanded that the dinosaur be contained and closely monitored. However, Dr. Rodriguez argued that the T-Rex deserved the chance to thrive in its own natural habitat.',4),(49,24,'After much deliberation, a plan was devised to transport the T-Rex back to the past where it belonged. It was a risky and complex operation that required the use of advanced technology. The Resurrecto-Tron 3000 was modified to create a time portal, allowing the T-Rex to return to its prehistoric era.',5),(50,24,'On the day of the transfer, crowds gathered to witness the historic event. The Resurrecto-Tron 3000 hummed to life, and a glowing portal appeared before them. The T-Rex hesitated at first, but then, as if sensing its true home, it bravely stepped through the portal and vanished from sight.',6),(51,24,'The success of the operation brought mixed emotions. While there was sadness at saying goodbye to the T-Rex, there was also a sense of relief knowing that the dinosaur was now safely back in its own time. Dr. Rodriguez and her team had achieved a remarkable feat in the field of science and technology, and the world would always remember the day when dinosaurs roamed the earth once again.',7),(52,25,'Once upon a time in a small town, there lived a boy named Alex. Alex loved to play soccer, and he dreamed of one day becoming a professional soccer player. Every day after school, Alex would gather his friends and they would all head to the park to play soccer. They would have so much fun kicking the ball around and pretending they were playing in the FIFA World Cup.',0),(53,25,'At the park, they would set up makeshift goalposts using their backpacks and sweatshirts. They would then divide into teams and play a fun and friendly game of soccer. Alex was always the captain of his team, and he loved the responsibility of leading his friends to victory. They would play for hours until the sun went down, and they could no longer see the ball. Those were some of the best times of Alex\'s life.',1),(54,25,'One day, the town decided to host a community soccer tournament at the park. Alex and his friends were so excited to participate. They formed a team and came up with a cool name, \"The Soccer Superstars.\" They practiced every day after school, perfecting their passing, dribbling, and shooting skills. They were determined to win the tournament and make their town proud.',2),(55,25,'The day of the tournament finally arrived. Families and friends from the town gathered at the park to watch the teams compete. The Soccer Superstars were up against some tough competition, but they were not afraid. They played with all their heart and showed incredible teamwork. With Alex leading the way, they won every match until they reached the final.',3),(56,25,'In the final match, the Soccer Superstars faced a team that had won the tournament for the past few years. The match was intense, and both teams played their best. The score was tied, and there were only a few minutes left on the clock. That\'s when Alex saw an opportunity and took a shot from far away. The ball soared through the air and landed in the opponent\'s goal, scoring the winning point for the Soccer Superstars.',4),(57,25,'The crowd erupted into cheers as the final whistle blew. The Soccer Superstars had won the tournament, and Alex couldn\'t believe it. He and his friends hugged and jumped with joy. Their hard work and dedication had paid off, and they were now the champions of the town\'s soccer tournament. They were even awarded a shiny trophy, and their names would forever be engraved on it.',5),(58,25,'From that day on, the Soccer Superstars became local heroes in their town. They continued to play soccer together, and Alex\'s dream of becoming a professional soccer player grew stronger. He knew that if he continued to work hard and never gave up, he could one day play in the FIFA World Cup and make his town even prouder.',6),(59,26,'Once upon a time, there was a kid named Max who loved to play the guitar. He would spend hours in his room, strumming the strings and trying to make up his own tunes. Max dreamed of becoming a rock star one day, playing in front of huge crowds and sharing his music with the world.',0),(60,26,'One day, Max\'s school announced that they were having a talent show. Max knew this was his chance to show everyone his skills. He decided to form a band with his friends. They practiced and practiced, and finally, the big day arrived. Max felt a little nervous as he stepped onto the stage, but as soon as he started playing, all his nerves vanished. The crowd went wild, cheering and clapping as the band rocked out.',1),(61,26,'After the talent show, Max\'s music teacher, Mrs. Reed, pulled him aside. \"Max, you have real talent,\" she said. \"I think it\'s time for you to take your music to the next level.\" Mrs. Reed told Max about a music camp that was held in the summer. It was a special camp where kids could learn from professional musicians and perform in a big concert at the end of the week.',2),(62,26,'Max was ecstatic! He begged his parents to let him go, and after much pleading, they finally agreed. The day of the camp arrived, and Max\'s eyes widened as he saw the beautiful campus and all the other kids who shared his passion for music. The days were filled with workshops and rehearsals, and Max soaked up every bit of knowledge like a sponge.',3),(63,26,'Finally, the day of the big concert arrived. Max and his bandmates were nervous, but once they started playing, all their worries melted away. They rocked the stage, and the audience erupted into cheers. Max felt like a real rock star, and he knew that this was just the beginning of his musical journey.',4),(64,26,'When Max returned home, he was bursting with inspiration. He started writing more songs and practicing even harder. He was determined to make his dream of becoming a rock star a reality. Max\'s dedication paid off, and soon, he and his band were performing at local venues and even getting noticed by record labels.',5),(65,26,'Max\'s journey to rock stardom wasn\'t always easy, but he never gave up on his passion for music. He continued to work hard and never stopped believing in himself. And as he stood on stage, playing his guitar and singing his heart out, Max knew that he had achieved his dream. He was a rock star, not just because of his talent, but because of his love for music and the unwavering determination that got him there.',6),(66,27,'Once upon a time in the small town of Riverdale, there was a famous museum that housed the most valuable jewels in the world. The museum was well-guarded with high-tech security systems, and people from all over the world came to see the precious jewels on display. But one day, a jewel thief managed to break into the museum and steal the most precious diamond, known as the Heart of the Ocean.',0),(67,27,'The townspeople were shocked and scared that such a thing could happen in their peaceful town. The police were called to investigate, but they had no leads. The mayor of Riverdale knew that something had to be done, so he called upon a group of young detectives to help solve the case.',1),(68,27,'The young detectives, known as the Mystery Solvers, were a group of kids who loved solving mysteries in their spare time. Their leader, Lily, was the smartest of them all. She always had a plan and was never afraid to take risks. Her friends, Alex, Emma, and Jake, were always by her side, ready to help crack the case.',2),(69,27,'The Mystery Solvers immediately accepted the challenge and went straight to the museum to investigate. They asked the museum staff if they had seen anything suspicious on the night of the robbery. The guards mentioned that they saw a shadowy figure lurking around the museum right before the alarm went off, but they couldn\'t make out who it was.',3),(70,27,'The young detectives searched the area and found a hidden door behind a large painting. It led to a secret passageway that nobody knew about. As they followed the passageway, they found themselves in an underground tunnel that seemed to lead outside the museum. They realized that this must have been the escape route used by the thief.',4),(71,27,'They followed the tunnel and came out to a small shed in the woods. Inside, they found a red glove with a small piece of diamond stuck to it. They knew that this was a clue left behind by the jewel thief.',5),(72,27,'Excited about their discovery, the Mystery Solvers went back to the museum to show the police what they had found. The police immediately took the glove for fingerprint analysis, hoping to find a match in their database. The town was buzzing with excitement, and everyone was hopeful that the thief would soon be caught.',6),(73,27,'Days went by, and there was no sign of the thief. The police were getting frustrated, and the town\'s people were losing hope. But the Mystery Solvers didn\'t give up. They continued to investigate and follow every lead they could find.',7),(74,27,'One afternoon, the police called the Mystery Solvers to the station. They had found a match for the fingerprints on the red glove. It belonged to a notorious jewel thief who had been on the run for years. The police immediately set out to find him, and with the help of the Mystery Solvers, they were able to track him down to an abandoned warehouse on the outskirts of town.',8),(75,27,'The thief was caught, and the precious diamond, the Heart of the Ocean, was returned to the museum. The town celebrated the bravery and intelligence of the young detectives, and the mayor declared them heroes of Riverdale. The Mystery Solvers had cracked the case and saved the day once again.',9),(76,28,'Once upon a time, in a land far away, there was a little girl named Lily who had a special pet. It wasn\'t a dog or a cat; it was a dragon! Lily’s pet dragon’s name was Spark, and he had shiny green scales and big, sparkly eyes. Spark could breathe fire and even fly, but he was the friendliest dragon you could ever meet.',0),(77,28,'Every day, Lily and Spark would go on adventures together. They explored the magical forest near their home, where they met all kinds of animals and insects. One day, they came across a family of bunnies who needed help. The bunnies had lost their home because of a big storm, and they didn\'t know where to go.',1),(78,28,'Lily and Spark decided to help the bunnies find a new place to live. They searched high and low, through the forest and across the meadow, until they found the perfect burrow for the bunnies. The bunnies were so happy and grateful, and they invited Lily and Spark to visit them anytime.',2),(79,28,'As they continued their adventures, Lily and Spark encountered all sorts of interesting bugs. They saw colorful butterflies fluttering in the air, busy bees collecting nectar from flowers, and even a curious little ladybug crawling on a leaf. Spark was fascinated by all the different bugs, and he even made friends with a friendly firefly named Flash.',3),(80,28,'One sunny afternoon, Lily and Spark stumbled upon a lost puppy in the forest. The puppy looked sad and scared, so Lily and Spark decided to help him find his way back home. They followed the puppy’s tracks until they came across a cozy little house in the clearing. The puppy\'s family was overjoyed to see him, and they thanked Lily and Spark for bringing him back safely.',4),(81,28,'As they journeyed on, Lily and Spark encountered more animals in need of their help. They helped a little bird build a new nest, rescued a squirrel stuck in a tree, and even saved a group of frogs from a muddy puddle. No matter what challenges they faced, Lily and Spark always worked together to help those in need.',5),(82,28,'One day, the king of the land heard about Lily and her pet dragon’s bravery and kindness. He invited them to the royal palace to honor their good deeds. Lily and Spark were thrilled to meet the king and queen, who thanked them for their selfless acts of kindness. The king even gave Spark a shiny medal for being the bravest and most helpful dragon in the kingdom.',6),(83,28,'After their visit to the palace, Lily and Spark continued their adventures, making new friends and helping those in need. They learned that no act of kindness is ever too small, and that even the smallest creatures can make a big difference in the world. And as they flew back home at the end of each day, Lily and Spark knew that they would always be there for each other, ready to face any challenge that came their way.',7),(84,29,'Once upon a time, in the not-too-distant future, a group of brave astronauts embarked on an incredible journey to explore outer space. Their mission was to travel to a distant planet beyond our solar system, using a revolutionary new spacecraft called the Starblazer. The Starblazer was equipped with the latest technology, allowing it to travel at speeds never before achieved by humans. As the astronauts boarded the spacecraft, they couldn\'t help but feel a mixture of excitement and nervousness. They were about to make history as the first humans to venture beyond the farthest reaches of our known universe.',0),(85,29,'\\nThe Starblazer lifted off from Earth with a deafening roar, leaving behind a trail of fire and smoke as it soared higher and higher into the sky. Inside the spacecraft, the astronauts floated in zero gravity, their faces lighting up with wonder as they gazed out of the windows at the vast expanse of space. The journey to the distant planet would take several years, so the astronauts spent their days conducting scientific experiments, maintaining the spacecraft, and training for the challenges that lay ahead.',1),(86,29,'\\nAs the Starblazer traveled deeper into space, the astronauts encountered phenomena that were beyond anything they had ever imagined. They observed the birth of new stars, witnessed the beauty of distant galaxies, and marveled at the wonders of the universe. Each new discovery filled them with a sense of awe and wonder, and they were reminded of the incredible diversity and vastness of the cosmos.',2),(87,29,'\\nOne day, as the Starblazer approached the distant planet, the astronauts prepared for the most crucial phase of their mission. They carefully navigated the spacecraft through a treacherous asteroid belt, using advanced navigation systems to avoid disaster. Finally, they arrived at their destination and gazed in awe at the alien world before them. The planet was a breathtaking sight, with its glowing red surface and swirling clouds of gas. The astronauts quickly got to work, deploying exploration drones to gather data and samples from the planet\'s surface.',3),(88,29,'\\nAs they explored the alien landscape, the astronauts made a remarkable discovery. They found evidence of primitive life forms, tiny microorganisms that thrived in the harsh conditions of the planet. This groundbreaking finding sent shockwaves through the scientific community back on Earth, opening up new possibilities for the search for extraterrestrial life. The astronauts celebrated their achievement, knowing that their journey had contributed to a greater understanding of the universe and our place within it.',4),(89,29,'\\nAfter completing their mission, the astronauts boarded the Starblazer and began the long journey back to Earth, carrying with them the knowledge and experiences they had gained from their incredible expedition. As they looked out of the windows at the stars and galaxies passing by, they knew that they had accomplished something truly extraordinary. Their adventure had not only pushed the boundaries of human exploration but had also inspired future generations to continue reaching for the stars.',5),(90,29,'\\nWhen the Starblazer finally returned to Earth, the astronauts were greeted as heroes, hailed for their courage, dedication, and the remarkable scientific discoveries they had made. Their mission had captured the imagination of people around the world, uniting them in a shared sense of wonder and curiosity about the mysteries of the universe. The story of the Starblazer and its brave crew became a symbol of humanity\'s endless quest for knowledge, adventure, and the relentless pursuit of the unknown.',6),(91,30,'Once upon a time, in the town of Maplewood, there was a group of kids who loved to make music together. They were all part of the school\'s marching band, a big group of students who played instruments and marched in parades and at football games. The band was known for being the best in the whole county, and everyone loved to watch them perform.',0),(92,30,'One day, the band director, Mr. Smith, announced that the band had been chosen to perform at the State Marching Band Festival. This was a huge honor, and everyone was thrilled. But there was a problem - they needed new uniforms. The old ones were worn out and shabby, and they just wouldn\'t do for such an important performance.',1),(93,30,'The band members knew that new uniforms would cost a lot of money, and the school didn\'t have enough in the budget to buy them. So, they decided to come up with a plan to raise the money themselves. They brainstormed ideas for fundraisers, and finally, they landed on a plan to organize a big concert in the town square and sell tickets to raise the money they needed. They were excited to have a chance to showcase their talents and creativity, and the whole town was eager to support them.',2),(94,30,'The day of the concert arrived, and the town square was filled with people. The band members were nervous but excited as they took the stage. They played a mix of songs, including some popular tunes and traditional marching band pieces. The crowd cheered and clapped along, and everyone had a great time. By the end of the concert, they had raised enough money for new uniforms, and they were overjoyed.',3),(95,30,'With the new uniforms purchased, the band members felt a renewed sense of pride and excitement. They practiced hard every day, making sure their performance would be perfect for the State Marching Band Festival. As the day of the festival approached, they felt a mix of nervousness and anticipation. They had worked so hard and put so much effort into their performance, and they wanted to do their very best.',4),(96,30,'When the day of the festival finally arrived, the band members put on their new uniforms and marched onto the field. The crowd cheered as they played their music and showed off their carefully choreographed moves. The judges were impressed, and when the results were announced, the Maplewood Marching Band had won first place! The whole town celebrated their victory, and the band members were filled with pride and joy.',5),(97,30,'The band director congratulated the students on their hard work and dedication. He reminded them that it was their creativity, teamwork, and determination that had made their success possible. The band members felt a sense of accomplishment and unity, knowing that they had achieved something amazing together.',6),(98,30,'From that day on, the Maplewood Marching Band continued to perform at events and parades, inspiring others with their art and creativity. They learned that by working together and using their talents, they could achieve great things. The band became a symbol of the power of teamwork and the joy of making music, and they were proud to share their passion with the world.',7),(99,31,'Once upon a time, there was a boy named Alex who loved playing ice hockey. He had been playing since he was six years old and loved everything about the sport. From skating fast on the ice to scoring goals, Alex couldn\'t get enough of it. He played for a local team called the Ice Dragons and they had a big game coming up against their rivals, the Frosty Falcons.',0),(100,31,'Every day after school, Alex would rush to the ice rink to practice with his team. They would work on passing, shooting, and skating drills to make sure they were ready for the game. Alex\'s favorite part of practice was when they got to scrimmage against each other. He loved the feeling of gliding across the ice and trying to outmaneuver his teammates to score a goal.',1),(101,31,'On the day of the big game, Alex was so excited. He put on his gear and laced up his skates, ready to hit the ice. The arena was filled with the sound of cheering fans and the smell of hot chocolate from the concession stand. The Ice Dragons and the Frosty Falcons took their positions on the ice, ready to battle it out.',2),(102,31,'The game was intense, with both teams playing their hearts out. Alex\'s team was down by one goal in the final period, and he knew he had to give it his all. With just a few minutes left on the clock, Alex raced down the ice with the puck, weaving through the opposing team\'s defense. He took a shot and...scored! The crowd erupted into cheers as Alex tied the game.',3),(103,31,'The game went into overtime, and both teams fought hard to try and score the winning goal. Finally, with just a minute left, Alex found himself with the puck again. He took a deep breath, focused, and shot the puck with all his might. The puck sailed into the net, and the buzzer sounded. The Ice Dragons had won the game, thanks to Alex\'s winning goal.',4),(104,31,'After the game, Alex was beaming with joy. He was so proud of his team and himself for their hard-fought victory. The coach congratulated them all for their teamwork and determination. As they skated off the ice, Alex couldn\'t wait to celebrate with his teammates.',5),(105,31,'His love for ice hockey had brought him so much joy and excitement, and he couldn\'t wait to see what adventures the sport would bring him in the future.',6),(106,32,'Once upon a time, in the deep blue sea, there lived a friendly shark named Sammy. Sammy was not like the scary sharks in the movies. He was kind and loved to make new friends. One day, Sammy met a group of colorful fish. They were a little scared of Sammy at first, but he showed them that he was nice and just wanted to play. The fish and Sammy became the best of friends, swimming and playing games together every day. \\n\nOne sunny morning, Sammy and his fish friends noticed something strange. There was a big, shiny object floating in the water. It turned out to be a treasure chest! They all swam over to the chest and opened it. Inside, they found shiny pearls and glittering jewels. They were amazed at the shiny treasure and had so much fun playing with it. The fish and Sammy decided to share the treasure with all the sea creatures, making everyone happy. \\n\nAs the days went by, more and more sea animals heard about the kind shark and his treasure. They all wanted to be friends with Sammy and play with the shiny jewels. The sea turtle, octopus, and even the tiny seahorses all wanted to join in the fun. Sammy was thrilled to have so many new friends and loved showing them around the sea. \\n\nOne day, the sea creatures noticed that the coral reef was looking dull and grey. The beautiful colors were fading away, and the fish were sad. Sammy and his friends knew they had to do something to help. They organized a big clean-up day, where they all worked together to pick up the trash and make the coral reef beautiful again. Everyone was so happy to see the reef sparkling with color once more. Sammy and his friends had saved the day! \\n\nFrom that day on, the sea creatures had even more fun together. They would play hide and seek in the coral, have races with the seahorses, and have picnics on the sandy ocean floor. Sammy was the happiest shark in the sea, knowing that he had so many wonderful friends and that they all made the ocean a better place.',0),(107,33,'Once upon a time in New York City, there was a talented painter named Lily. She lived in a small apartment in the bustling city, where she spent her days painting beautiful pictures. Lily\'s paintings were filled with vibrant colors and unique designs that captivated anyone who saw them. She dreamt of one day having her own art exhibit in a big gallery, where people from all over the world could come and admire her work.',0),(108,33,'Every morning, Lily would wake up early and head to the park to find inspiration for her paintings. She loved to watch the golden sunlight shining